SLIDE 2 — Set the Tone: Acknowledge Reality
Let’s Start with the Truth
Many complex projects do deliver successfully today
Delivery succeeds because of:
strong Product Owners
experienced architects
committed engineers
intense manual coordination
This organization already knows how to deliver
Key message
Success exists — but it is expensive and fragile.
Diagram prompt
“Diagram showing successful project delivery held together by many human hands, calls, chats, and meetings.
